title: Wednesday Pt2: Trey Lance Questions, Hall of Famer Alan Faneca, Playmakers in Week 3, and British Celebs
itunes:title: Wednesday Pt2: Trey Lance Questions, Hall of Famer Alan Faneca, Playmakers in Week 3, and British Celebs
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with questions around the 49ers protection of Trey Lance. Hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty debate the thoughts on an offensive scheme endangering a player.  Hall of Famer Alan Faneca helps preview Thursday's Steelers/Browns matchup before we ask which player will need to have the ball most in Week 3.  With the show going overseas, the table suggests British celebs they would like to have join them on the set.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
